
    Perl 5 module Mail::Sendmail

Mail::Sendmail is a pure perl module that provides a simple
platform-independent mailer.

INSTALLATION

You install Mail::Sendmail by running these commands in the *nix environment:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test (optional)
   make install

If you have a CPAN client installed, you should be able to run something like:

   cpan Mail::Sendmail
   cpanm Mail::Sendmail

DOCUMENTATION

POD format documentation is included in lib/IO/Tee.pm.
You can read the documentation online:

    https://metacpan.org/pod/Mail::Sendmail

Or read it on your terminal, using the perldoc command:

    perldoc Mail::Sendmail

